@startuml
title ATM - PIN Validation and Transaction Processing

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state WaitingForCustomerChoice
state ProcessingRequest
state Ejecting
state Confiscating

Idle : entry / Display Welcome

Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForCustomerChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN / Confiscate

WaitingForCustomerChoice --> ProcessingRequest : Request Selected / Process Request
WaitingForCustomerChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

ProcessingRequest --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject
ProcessingRequest --> ProcessingRequest : Processing Complete / Continue

Ejecting --> Idle : Card Ejected / Display Ejected
Confiscating --> Idle : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated

@enduml
